{"tid":331549,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自稱「黃絲」男為薪酬投考警察　盼扶正警隊名聲","createTime":"2017-07-22T09:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T12:51:23.000Z","uid":119494,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb19021f051bb6fb3979adb305fb57195b43c62","tid":331549,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"警隊今舉行夏季招募日，有逾2600人投考，人數比去年上升3.4%，更為2010年後新高。有曾參與佔中的年輕人前來面試，直言自己被薪酬待遇所吸引；亦有人屢敗屢戰，三度投考警察。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的王先生自稱是「黃絲」，3年前曾參與佔中，他覺得前線警員當時是「傀儡、被淪為政治工具」，但他直言被警隊薪酬吸引，故報考督察。有見近年警隊屢受批評，他稱若自己成功投考督察，希望能夠扶正警隊名聲，但他不認同警員私下使用武力。<br />\n被問到是否擔心他日會在街頭與抗爭的朋友對峙，王先生指自己會理解對方想法：「我不會反對他所爭取的，我會感到難受，但維持治安始終是我的工作職責。」<br />\n<br />\n三度投考督察的賴先生稱，自己一直有志加入警隊，惟過去兩次都在遴選委員會中落選，「今次投考自信心大了，但會以平常心面對結果」。28歲的他現職商界銷售員，但他認為警隊工作更有意義和挑戰性，故希望轉行。<br />\n<br />\n他指，警隊整體對香港繁榮穩定作出貢獻，而負面新聞只佔小部分，故不願評論個別警員濫權事件。<br />\n<br />\n署理警察招募組警司郭志濠指，今季有逾2600人投考警隊，見習督察平均40人爭一位，警員則10人競爭一職位。他強調，投考者需「有心服務社會，有才能，及價值觀與警隊相近」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e7a55af99f0cf64f2bbd61b17f4200e994aef5","tid":331549,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"一千蚊都deal，唔通兩皮幾嘢唔deal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9903741d36b4be00eb5cce5a647c1c908b602f1a","tid":331549,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"係都唔好同人講啦"},{"pid":"f6dc9f9847f60cb43b4a7d7cf9e628c417f19e21","tid":331549,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"我唔反對，但我會打柒你"},{"pid":"f8f302dabe6a8164a8dff52f698c8af37c23cd19","tid":331549,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db49e39440538df109b17a511ebce52539afeb8c","tid":331549,"uid":113956,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一千蚊都deal，唔通兩皮幾嘢唔deal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊督察呀<br />\n起薪40k 做幾年穩升SIP 80k走唔甩<br />\n<br />\nPC仔就算9數 日日行出街比人屌 平均壽命又短 都係得果2,30k 真係垃圾先做"},{"pid":"af7ee3e5666e382946cb0619d83c5db1afb913b9","tid":331549,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"鴨"},{"pid":"8624790fc169b3109ad2153f5e7a83e38781ee92","tid":331549,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07